Package net.novazero.lib.ikbus.io

I/O related interfaces and classes for reading and writing I/K-bus packets.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IKBusConnection
    Interface for classes that provide a communication link between the application and an I/K-bus.
    IKBusPacketReader
    Interface for classes that can provide a reader for a stream of I/K-bus packets.
    IKBusPacketStreamElement
    Interface used to represent data elements read from an I/K-bus communication link.
    IKBusPacketWriter
    Interface for classes that can provide a writer for a stream of I/K-bus packets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InputStreamIKBusPacketReader
    An I/K-bus packet reader that reads and parses its data from an input stream.
    InvalidIKBusPacketStreamElement
    Implementation of the IKBusPacketStreamElement interface to represent invalid I/K-bus packet stream elements.
    TimeRestrictedInputStream
    An input stream wrapper class used for creating an input stream whose read calls can timeout.
    ValidIKBusPacketStreamElement
    Implementation of the IKBusPacketStreamElement interface to represent valid I/K-bus packet stream elements.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IKBusIOException
    Exception that will be thrown when an error occurs while reading or writing I/K-bus data.

Package net.novazero.lib.ikbus.io Description

I/O related interfaces and classes for reading and writing I/K-bus packets.
